long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Customize your new tab with the popular cars wallpaper extension and display your favorite cars in the background.
Beautify your new tab page with a useful, beautiful and fun theme.
JDM Cars Wallpaper New Tab is here to enhance your new tab experience.
Choose the background theme of your favorite cars, make your daily trip quickly thanks to the social media icons.

All in one tab.

Click 'ADD TO CHROME' to install the JDM Cars Wallpaper New Tab extension.

Main Features:
* Choose from among many fastest cars background images and change them
* Select preferred background change feature from settings menu
* Quickly access your social media accounts
* Popular games menu for fun
* Follow the time, date and day information from the top right
* Search the internet quickly and accurately using the search box in the middle top

Note: For the best experience, click the "Keep changes" button after installing JDM Cars Wallpaper New Tab. This will show JDM Cars Wallpaper Theme on every new tab as intended.

➤ Search Box: You can use the search box in the middle to search on the website www.tabssearch.com and access search results provided by Google. www.tabssearch.com is a search engine website designed for the best results. Enter your search terms, and the most relevant results will be displayed instantly. To see more detailed results, narrow down your search for social media, images, news, videos, music, shopping, etc.

In your image searches, you can use the multiple filter features to find the desired image more quickly. The image search filters include License, File Type, Color, Type, and more, allowing you to conduct detailed image searches.

➤ Background:
JDM Cars Wallpaper New Tab offers a selection of backgrounds with many games directly in the new tab. Change background images with few clicks from new tab.
